                Herculi <lb n="2"/>sacrum <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Plotius |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>VII <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Statuenbasis. Datierung: nicht vor 42 n. Chr., als die leg. VII den Beinamen p(ia) f(idelis) erhielt; sie war bis 56/57 n. Chr. in Dalmatien stationiert. (B): Jeličič, AE 1981, AE 1985: Abweichungen in Lesung / Ergänzung.</p>
            </div>
